建立外交、领事和商业关系」与中方对话"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f55a944be892e4f237b80da2c0020dd8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606637125"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IvIb+pe6/gL5YEAMaCDk3MDg4NTQxIPffpqQGMAA4pgJAKXIIOTcwODg1NDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1686949341.194726", "card_id": "Q_606454673", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本动画业界现在为什么再也出不了《EVA》，《攻壳机动队》，《星际牛仔》这样的里程碑式的作品了?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近几年基本没有以前那种兼具热度，深度，成熟度，超优剧情的现象级动漫了，而且可能以后也不会再有，最有希望的巨人也烂尾了。包括更之前的 EVA，钢炼 fa，死亡笔记，魔法少女小圆，银河英雄传说，阿基拉，clannad ，星际牛仔，高达，攻壳机动队等，这些具有艺术深度的动漫不知道什么时候能再看到。 庵野秀明很早就说过业界要完，但是关于什么时候要完却没有直接说明白，业界内很少有人能像痞子一样有权力手握脚本企划做 Eva 这样的作品了，大部分人只好顺应市场该做什么做什么，我也不确定是否能再出现下一个庵野秀明，宫崎骏，押井守，汤浅政明，富野，渡边信一郎这样的人。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-03054ccd66c163a27d6d505057680708_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606454673"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IvIb+pe6/gL5YEAMaCDk3MDQ4MDMzIInfoaQGMAA4vwFAKnIIOTcwNDgwMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1686949341.195263", "card_id": "Q_606951752", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 LPL 夏季赛 TES 2:0 击败 LGD，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-52e4c79bc670b760675d01f862cbc2ac_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url":